long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Tana Enhancer is a Chrome extension designed to enhance the user interface (UI) of the Tana application. This extension injects CSS styles from the Tana Nodes repository to improve the overall look and feel of the application. With Tana Enhancer, users can enjoy an customized experience while using Tana.
